### 6) Quick wiring checklist

- [ ] ESP32 3V3 → breadboard + rail
- [ ] ESP32 GND → breadboard - rail
- [ ] R1: + rail → bias node
- [ ] R2: bias node → - rail
- [ ] (Optional) C2: bias node → - rail
- [ ] C1: audio tip → bias node
- [ ] audio ground → - rail
- [ ] R3: bias node → ADC node
- [ ] ADC node → GPIO4 (or your configured ADC pin)
- [ ] (Optional) clamp diodes at ADC node

